<div class="accoladeDetail">
<p class="accoladeImage"><img src="http://textpattern.com/images/41.jpg" alt="Jon Hicks" width="51" height="51" /></p><p class="text">I’m always trying other solutions, but it just makes me love Textpattern more. It’s a system created for humans who crave a clean, non-intimidating and logical approach, but with great power and flexibility underneath. Deploying sites with Textpattern is a joy.</p>
</div> <!-- close accoladeDetail -->
</div> <!-- close accolade -->

<div class="accolade">
